[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1313","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1313.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1061","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10799,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10822}}","description":"HP Laserjet打印机配备JetDirect卡并配置TCP/IP时，默认未设置密码保护，未经身份验证的远程攻击者可直接连接打印机并篡改其IP地址或禁用日志记录功能。该漏洞影响所有使用JetDirect卡启用TCP/IP网络打印的HP Laserjet系列打印机设备。攻击者无需任何凭据即可通过Telnet或JetDirect服务连接目标打印机，修改网络配置导致打印服务中断或路由至恶意地址，同时关闭日志功能使安全审计失效。CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高。建议为JetDirect TCP/IP配置启用密码认证并限制访问来源。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1061"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.477","remediation":"为 HP JetDirect 卡启用并设置强管理员密码（通过打印机控制面板、JetDirect 嵌入式 Web 或 telnet 管理界面），禁止无密码 TCP/IP 配置；在边界防火墙/ACL 上限制仅管理网段可访问打印机 23/515/9099/9100 端口，并将设备划入隔离 VLAN，禁止公网及非必要网段直连；无法立即加固时，临时关闭远程管理并仅允许可信主机通过打印服务器转发任务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602248518480&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1876","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/431324351d69005e5e9ea9d116dc965ce92ed482/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1061.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1061","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1061.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1061.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4m74-673g-77xx/GHSA-4m74-673g-77xx.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/passwordless_lexmark_printer.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2012/gb_hp_jet_direct_unauthenticated_access.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1061.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87933/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1313.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0160","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0160.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0061","title":"BSD Line Printer Daemon (lpd) 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 行式打印机守护进程（lpd）存在远程代码执行漏洞，源于其对打印任务处理过程中缺乏充分的访问控制与输入验证。远程攻击者无需认证即可向运行 lpd 服务的目标系统发送特制的打印请求，实现任意文件创建、删除或远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Linux 及 BSD 系列操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0061"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.180","remediation":"禁用 lpd 服务（`killall lpd` 并移除启动项），升级到已修复版本，或使用 TCP Wrapper 限制端口 515 仅允许受信主机访问；对于不需要网络打印的系统，建议直接卸载 lpd 替代为 CUPS 或 LPRng 等现代打印系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0061"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0160.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1402","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1402.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1213","title":"HP HP-UX 10.30 Telnet 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.30 操作系统的 Telnet 远程登录服务存在输入验证缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络向目标主机的 Telnet 端口（TCP 23）发送特制畸形数据包，触发 Telnet 守护进程异常退出，导致服务拒绝访问。该漏洞影响运行 HP-UX 10.30 版本的 HP 工作站与服务器，攻击者无需任何凭据即可在低复杂度条件下完成攻击，造成受影响系统上合法用户无法通过 Telnet 进行远程管理，危害等级为中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1213"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.627","remediation":"升级至 HP-UX 11.0 或更高版本（已修复该 Telnet 服务拒绝服务漏洞），或应用 HP 官方发布的 PHNE_19002 补丁。若暂时无法升级，建议在防火墙层面限制 Telnet 端口 (23/tcp) 仅允许受信 IP 访问，或禁用 Telnet 服务改用 SSH 替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www2.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1997_4/0001.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/571","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/457d74301bd08d78bede177295a6ca646467d2a7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1213.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1213","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1213.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/fb79aaf8eeeb3ec551114292cd7a8693e166aee6/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1213.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xcq8-4f2m-85q2/GHSA-xcq8-4f2m-85q2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87998/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1213.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--ce266dea-2c15-4359-a749-2880ad7d1d5e.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1402.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0541","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0326","title":"HP HP-UX mediainit 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 mediainit 媒体设备初始化程序存在安全漏洞。该程序用于初始化磁带机等存储设备，但由于对输入参数缺乏充分验证，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷，通过向 mediainit 程序传递特制参数触发漏洞，导致系统机密信息部分泄露、系统数据被部分篡改或服务部分不可用。此漏洞为本地利用，无需额外认证，攻击复杂度低，影响 HP-UX 系统多个版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。HP 已通过安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0326"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.543","remediation":"立即应用 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供的官方补丁。如无法打补丁，可移除 mediainit 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mediainit），并限制可执行权限仅授予信任的管理员用户组。建议将 HP-UX 系统升级至包含该修复的后续版本（如 11.0 以上），因 10.x 系列已终止技术支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9710-071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0497","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0300","title":"Sun Solaris NIS+ nis_cachemgr 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 缓存管理器存在安全设计缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向缓存中注入恶意的 NIS+ 服务器信息。当客户端查询网络信息服务时，将连接到攻击者控制的伪造服务器，导致敏感信息（如用户凭据、主机配置）被窃取或服务遭到劫持。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0300"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.247","remediation":"针对 Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 漏洞，建议立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #155 中提供的官方补丁。如运行 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 且无法打补丁，应在网络边界通过防火墙限制对 nis_cachemgr 端口（TCP/UDP 387）的访问，仅允许受信 NIS+ 服务器通信。由于 NIS+ 已停止维护，建议迁移至基于 LDAP 的命名服务以获得长期安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/155","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0300","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0300.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--12792e2d-cd40-4418-b42c-679d4e4e14e3.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0458","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0272","title":"Slmail POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Slmail 3.0.2421 及 2.5 版本的 POP3 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标主机的 POP3 端口（默认 110）发送特制恶意数据包，导致服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成正常的邮件收发功能中断。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需复杂权限即可触发，影响运行 Slmail 服务的邮件服务器系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0272"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.843","remediation":"Slmail 产品已停止维护多年，建议迁移至现代受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exchange 等）。如仍需继续使用，可在防火墙层面限制 POP3 端口（110）仅允许受信任 IP 段访问，并监控异常连接流量作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0213","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0090","title":"IBM AIX rcp 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 系统 rcp 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 rcp 命令提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。利用需要本地用户身份，成功利用后攻击者可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0090"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.733","remediation":"IBM 已在 AIX 4.x 版本的 APAR IY09308 中修复此漏洞，建议更新 bos.rte.net_filesystem fileset 至包含该 APAR 的维护级别。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/bin/rcp 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/rcp，或禁用 r-commands 服务（rshd、rexecd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0090"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0490","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0490.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0295","title":"Sun Solaris sysdef 命令本地内核内存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 sysdef 命令存在内核内存信息泄露漏洞。本地普通用户可通过执行 sysdef 命令读取内核内存中的敏感数据，进而获取内核地址布局等关键信息，结合其他漏洞可导致权限提升至 root 级别。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4/2.5/2.5.1 及 SunOS 5.3-5.5.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。Sun 已发布安全公告 157 提供修复方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0295"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin 157 提供的官方补丁。鉴于 SunOS 5.3~5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.4~2.5.1 均已停止维护，建议升级到受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11.4 或更高版本。如无法升级，临时缓解措施为：以 root 权限执行 chmod 700 /usr/sbin/sysdef 限制 sysdef 命令的访问权限，仅允许 root 用户执行，同时移除 sysdef 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/sysdef），防止本地普通用户通过该命令读取内核内存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0490.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0368","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0368.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0185","title":"Sun SunOS/Solaris FTP 服务数据端口信任滥用远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 FTP 服务与 rlogin 服务之间存在信任关系绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可利用 FTP 协议的数据端口（20/tcp）主动连接至目标主机上受信任的 rlogin 服务，绕过正常认证机制实现远程命令执行。该漏洞源于 FTP 服务器被目标主机配置为信任主机，攻击者无需任何凭证即可通过构造特殊 FTP 会话获得对目标系统的完全控制，影响 SunOS 5.3~5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.3~2.5.1 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0185"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #156 提供的对应 Solaris 版本补丁。停止使用 rlogin/rsh 服务，改用 SSH 进行远程管理；删除 /etc/hosts.equiv 及所有用户的 .rhosts 文件以消除主机间隐式信任关系；配置 FTP 服务禁止 PORT 命令反弹连接至非 FTP 端口（如在 wu-ftpd 中设置 refuse-connection 规则），阻断反弹攻击路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0368.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0329","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0329.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0160","title":"Cisco IOS PPP CHAP 认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 设备的 PPP CHAP 认证机制存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用该漏洞建立未授权的 PPP 连接，从而获得目标网络的访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露、数据篡改或服务中断。该漏洞影响多款经典 Cisco IOS 设备，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互，CVSS v2 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0160"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.1 或更高版本（该漏洞已在 11.1 及后续维护版本中修复）。如无法立即升级，可在 PPP 接口配置 `access-class` ACL 限制仅允许可信源 IP 建立拨号连接，并在全局配置下使用 `no service tcp-small-servers` 和 `no service udp-small-servers` 关闭不必要的小型服务以减小攻击面。对于仍在运行不受支持老版本 IOS 的设备，建议迁移至当前受支持的 IOS 版本或替换为现代网络设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0329.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0363","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0182","title":"Samba Samba 1.9.19 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 1.9.19 及更早版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 Samba 服务发送特制的超长密码字符串触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 Samba 1.9.19 的 Unix/Linux 系统，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0182"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.523","remediation":"立即升级 Samba 至 2.0.0 及以上版本（1.9.19 系列已停止维护，2.0.0 修复了该缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法立即升级，可在 smb.conf 中设置 hosts allow/deny 限制可访问 SMB 服务的源 IP 范围，并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 139 和 445 的外部访问以临时缓解风险。现代 Linux 发行版应直接使用系统包管理器更新至当前受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-110.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20308","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0182.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0182","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/292.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/02ed2a2b96fc19fd49a4be810f3493abb776ec4e/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0470","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0282","title":"（已废弃）CVE-1999-0282 错误合并 SunOS loadmodule 两个独立漏洞的无效编号","description":"CVE-1999-0282 是一个已被官方驳回（REJECTED）的 CVE 编号，原因是它错误地将 CVE-1999-1584 和 CVE-1999-1586 两个不同漏洞的参考信息和描述合并为一条记录。NVD 已移除该编号下所有描述与引用，禁止继续使用。该编号不指向任何真实存在的漏洞，不存在可利用的攻击面或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0282"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:56.640","remediation":"CVE-1999-0282 已被撤销，请勿使用此编号。实际漏洞分别对应 CVE-1999-1584（SunOS 4.1.1–4.1.3c 及 Open Windows 3.0 中 loadmodule/modload 的本地权限提升）和 CVE-1999-1586（SunOS 4.1.x 中 xnews 调用的 loadmodule 未正确清理环境变量导致本地提权）。Sun 当时发布了补丁（如 Sun patch 100124-01），CERT 也发布了公告 CA-1993-18，但这些补丁现已无法获取。由于 SunOS 4.x 早已停止支持，建议将仍在运行的 SunOS 4.1.x 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Solaris 11、Linux 或 \\*BSD），同时严格控制 setuid/setgid 二进制文件的权限以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0452","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0267","title":"NCSA HTTPd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.3 版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，进而实现远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0267"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.227","remediation":"NCSA HTTPd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。迁移后需重新配置虚拟主机、访问控制和 SSL 证书，并关闭旧服务器上的 80/443 端口。如无法立即迁移，可在防火墙层面限制对 80 端口的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0267","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21050","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0267","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-1999-0267.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1237","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1237.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0955","title":"wu-ftpd和BSDI ftpd SITE EXEC命令竞争条件漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd和BSDI ftpd在处理SITE EXEC命令时存在竞争条件漏洞。远程攻击者可通过发送特制的SITE EXEC请求，在竞争窗口内利用条件竞争绕过权限检查，从而获取root用户权限，完全控制目标服务器。该漏洞攻击复杂度较高，但成功利用后危害极大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0955"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-09-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复该漏洞的wu-ftpd或BSDI ftpd版本，或禁用SITE EXEC命令。对于已停止维护的系统，建议迁移至更安全的FTP服务器软件如vsftpd，并限制FTP服务的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T04:28:25.803299151+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0955"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1237.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1249","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1249.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0965","title":"X.Org xterm 日志选项竞争条件本地文件修改漏洞","description":"xterm 的日志功能（logging option）存在竞争条件漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用该竞争条件，在日志文件写入过程中篡改目标文件的符号链接或内容，从而实现向任意文件写入数据的目的。该漏洞影响使用 xterm 终端的类 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地登录权限或 shell 访问能力才能触发利用。成功利用可导致本地权限提升或对系统文件进行未授权修改，危害等级中等。建议升级 xterm 至最新版本，并在多用户环境中合理配置终端权限以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0965"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.353","remediation":"升级 xterm 至 Patch #131（2000/03/03 发布）或更高版本，该补丁将 creat_as() 函数中的 O_APPEND 替换为 O_EXCL，并在打开日志文件后增加所有权和写权限校验，从而消除日志选项中的竞争条件。如无法立即升级，可临时通过 X 资源文件将 xterm 的 logfile 选项设为禁用状态，或在终端启动参数中取消 -l 选项以关闭日志功能，避免本地用户利用竞争窗口篡改任意文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0965","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/20b9340dcaffca733259fb153ac741206a5bbc5f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0965.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0965","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/b6ed432383ec9e70047ae649904e3a43ee847c40/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-oe/recipes-graphics/xorg-app/xterm_410.bb","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0965.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e90735e3e31fc62018265dfbae313d166e653462/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0965.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3vvm-3j5j-gc9q/GHSA-3vvm-3j5j-gc9q.json","https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded/blob/e93799db0e7c7b23da8a00891403425ae7e87d7b/meta-oe/recipes-graphics/xorg-app/xterm_410.bb","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://g